否把锂电池的温度降低到热失控的阈值以下，让电池停止热失控和热扩散。 那么在多数灭火剂的选项中，自然应当选择降温效果最好的，也就是：水。 锂电池燃烧会释放氧气这一特点，也正是电动车火灾如此难以扑灭的主要原因。"},"attached_info":"CkAI/Jj3mLCY1c0nEAMaCTEwNTExNDI5MyDa9fitBjAAONABQBxyCTY0Mjc2NTEwNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/697920c8d378b9cd36b0dac7b85e75e3_xl.jpg?source=c885d018"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1716597908.923079","card_id":"Q_656870197","target":{"id":656870197,"title":"为什么老员工不愿意带新人了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/656870197","type":"question","created":1716415232,"answer_count":135,"follower_count":199,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2566,5442,27919],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI/Jj3mLCY1c0nEAMaCTEwODI0OTIyMCCA1rmyBjAAOMcBQB1yCTY1Njg3MDE5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-9cc746de03ac4abbf23479670db3360a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1716597908.923295","card_id":"Q_656902748","target":{"id":656902748,"title":"「松弛感」是 2024 年的消费者主流价值观之一吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/656902748","type":"question","created":1716432839,"answer_count":57,"follower_count":87,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[735,2016,12513,41187,3507217],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I/Jj3mLCY1c0nEAMaCTEwODI1NjQyMiDH37qyBjAAOFdAHnIJNjU2OTAyNzQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"26 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ed18754e239811daca5f1c67e308c60c_b